{{Infobox holiday |holiday_name = Book Lovers Day |type = International |official_name = National Book Lovers Day |nickname = BLD |duration = 1 day |frequency = Annual |observedby = All |date = August 9 |celebrations = |relatedto = }}
'''Book Lovers Day''' (aka '''National Book Lovers Day''' in the US) is celebrated on August 9 every year.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cbs19.tv/video/news/local/national-book-lovers-day-on-the-morning-loop/501-8214828|title=National Book Lovers Day on the Morning Loop|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.print.de/news-de/der-9-august-ist-der-tag-der-buchliebhaber|title=Der 9. August ist der Tag der Buchliebhaber|date=9 August 2018|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yjS2ZWwjMcw|title=National book lovers day|first=|last=FOX 4 Now|date=9 August 2017|publisher=|via=YouTube}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.freepressjournal.in/indore/national-book-lovers-day-today-readers-find-solace-in-comics-philosophy-and-fiction/1331652|title=National Book Lover's Day Today: Readers find solace in comics, philosophy and fiction - Free Press Journal|date=9 August 2018|publisher=}}</ref> This is an unofficial holiday observed to encourage bibliophiles celebrate reading and literature. People are advised to put away their smartphones and every possible technological distraction and pick up a book to read. Book Lovers Day is widely recognized on global scale yet its origin and creator remains unknown to date.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.deccanchronicle.com/lifestyle/books-and-art/090818/book-lovers-day-authors-share-more-about-their-favourite-reads.html|title=Book Lovers Day: Authors share more about their favorite reads|date=9 August 2018|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://heavy.com/news/2017/08/national-book-lovers-day-2017-facts-origin-date/|title=National Book Lovers Day 2017: 5 Fast Facts You Need to Know|first=Daniel S.|last=Levine|date=9 August 2017|publisher=}}</ref>
